column2: STATcube – Statistical Database of STATISTICS AUSTRIA

.) Subject of the statistics: Statistics on bovine livestock as of 1993 held on livestock holdings in Austria. .) Current legal basis: Regulation (EC) No 1165/2008 of 19 November 2008 concerning livestock and meat statistics National legal basis BGBl II No. 163/2012 .) Updating: Time series adjustment three months after the reference dates 1 June and 1 December of each calendar year. Last update: [2023-08-24] .) Contact details: Directorate Spatial Statistics - Animal Production, Consumer Health Information System Martina Wiesinger, Tel. +43 1 71128 - 7959 tiere@statistik.gv.at Other Metadata: https://statistik.gv.at/en/statistics/agriculture-and-forestry/animals-animal-production/livestock/annual-livestock

Data on “Cows in total” only were published as the result of the 1 December 1997 Census. For the purpose of receiving consistent numerical series results for “dairy cows” and “other cows” were interpolated.
